{
  "stem": "16214.3",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because to some degree, I believe that why-- why do we have such open society here in the United States?",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Jews don't live in ghettos.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They don't isolate themselves.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I know that a lot of it was historically because Jews could not live anyplace they wanted to, or Jews could not buy land.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I understand all that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But to some degree, it is incredible to me that Jews would be living from 1430, like my father's documents show, which I have-- and they would not learn the language properly.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I mean, it's-- it's beyond belief.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But a lot of Jews spoke Polish so poorly that you could not believe it.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They basically were totally-- they were isolating themselves in a lot of ways.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And I think that fostered the prejudices as well.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And I am against that.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I hope the society is open both ways.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You're quite welcome.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And thank you for letting me say what I had to say.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
